  "message": "fnp-conformance: expand FNP-P2C-005 adversarial ufunc corpus\n\nAdd three new adversarial cases to broaden packet FNP-P2C-005 coverage:\n\n- add_broadcast_middle_dim_conflict_2x3x4_vs_2x5x4\n  Exercises mixed-rank/middle-axis broadcast rejection for binary add.\n- sum_axis_out_of_bounds_large_keepdims_2x3x4\n  Exercises large out-of-range axis handling with keepdims=true.\n- sum_axis_out_of_bounds_rank_two_2x1_axis_2\n  Exercises hardened-mode axis bounds rejection at ndim boundary.\n\nAll cases preserve packet metadata and artifact references so workflow-scenario and adversarial harness logging contracts stay intact.\n\nValidation run (with rch offload for cargo commands):\n- rch exec -- cargo test -p fnp-conformance ufunc_adversarial_suite_is_green -- --nocapture\n- rch exec -- cargo run -p fnp-conformance --bin run_workflow_scenario_gate\n- rch exec -- cargo check --workspace --all-targets\n- rch exec -- cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings\n- rch exec -- cargo fmt --check\n- UBS_MAX_DIR_SIZE_MB=0 ubs --diff",
